Class TokenRequestMessage

java.lang.Object
  messaging.AbstractMessage
      messaging.TokenRequestMessage

public class TokenRequestMessage
extends AbstractMessage

A TokenRequestMessage is a message sent between gates requesting tokens from their respective dates.
